{"title":"杏核儿","authors":["王宜振"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":1,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"杏核儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王宜振"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要写一首小诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一首关于春天的小诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你思考了很长一段时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不知道怎样下笔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我递给你一颗杏核儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说，把它种下去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗就长出来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许我们的土地贫瘠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗很小很瘦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们记住了浇水的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们记住了施肥的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月诗是红的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四月诗是绿的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月呢，是金黄的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来，我们都醉了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醉倒在诗的怀抱里"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}